title: Drawing, "Female Head, Left Profile: Ida Lupino"
description: In the present profile, on the top half of the page, a thick line describes the outline, extending from the top of the forehead to the faintly sketched vertical line of the neck. To the right, Ida/ Lupino is inscribed in capitals. In the upper right hand corner, in script, are the lines She ruthlessly suppressed/ his bad points. Additional writing, also in script, reads Miss/ Dee/ Burton (?) Evan (?).
